        {
            "id": 5908259,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 深證成指下跌-217.56點至10661.9248點，跌幅2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間21日02:01，深證成指下跌217.56點（或2%），暫報10661.92點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.33%</li><li>近 1 月：+0.79%</li><li>近 3 月：+2.19%</li><li>近 6 月：+34.73%</li><li>今年以來：+4.46%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>兩輪車概念領跌-5.26%。其中    信隆健康(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002105:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002105\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002105-CN</a>)            下跌        10.01%            ;        星星科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300256:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300256\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300256-CN</a>)            下跌        9.38%            ;        深中華A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000017-CN</a>)            下跌        3.44%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華為汽車概念領跌-4.11%。其中    光弘科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300735:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300735\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300735-CN</a>)            下跌        8.98%            ;        富臨精工(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300432:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300432\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300432-CN</a>)            下跌        8.75%            ;        祥鑫科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002965:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002965\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002965-CN</a>)            下跌        8.02%    。</p></section></main>",
