        {
            "id": 5907316,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉「骯髒15國」低氣壓籠罩 權值股低調 跌168點失守年線",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台灣被川普政府列為對美徵收高額關稅的「骯髒 15 國」(the dirty 15)，台股今 (21) 日籠罩低氣壓，權值股無力延續昨 (20) 日漲勢，大盤終場跌 168.16 點或 0.75%，以 22209.10 點作收，年線得而復失，成交量放大至 3167 億元。輝達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 宣布推出矽光子共同封裝光學 (CPO) 網路交換器，激勵矽光子族群今天續強。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股今天大多下挫，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 跌逾 1%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 跌 0.6%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 跌 0.34%。另外，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 跌 0.39%，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 跌 0.92%，僅台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 小漲 0.64%。金融權值股今天也臉黑，國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>)、富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>) 也有 1% 左右的跌幅。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台塑四寶今天臉綠，台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>)、南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>) 跌逾 4%，台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%，台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>) 跌逾 2%。其他塑膠類股也走弱，台聚 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1304:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1304\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1304-TW</a>)、華夏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1305:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1305\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1305-TW</a>)、聯成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1313-TW</a>) 跌逾 4%，國喬 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1312:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1312\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1312-TW</a>)、中石化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1314:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1314\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1314-TW</a>) 跌逾 2%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鋼鐵類股今天表現弱勢，新鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2032:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2032\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2032-TW</a>) 跌逾半根停板，中鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2014:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2014\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2014-TW</a>)、大成鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2027-TW</a>) 跌逾 4%，官田鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2017-TW</a>)、允強 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2034:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2034\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2034-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>輝達執行長黃仁勳宣布推出 Spectrum-X 及 Quantum-X 矽光子共同封裝光學 (CPO) 網路交換器，激勵矽光子及網通族群今天表現亮眼，矽光子方面，直接獲輝達點名的波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>) 亮燈漲停，全新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2455:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2455\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2455-TW</a>)、上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>)、昇達科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3491:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3491\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3491-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>網通族群部分，智邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，中磊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5388:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5388\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5388-TW</a>)、啟碁 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6285:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6285\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6285-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，眾達 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>) 也有超過 1% 的漲幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
